[This is an old problem when one has striking numerator events and
the denominator is either ignored or so small as to distort any
comparisons. In veterinary medicine I have not seen any specific
reports of negative impacts on livestock in the literature or from
farmers, and God knows we vaccinate more cows than the military its
solders. Plus we now have plenty of women in the military. It was a
regular question I would be asked when lecturing to the US Air
National Guard about being vaccinated and an obvious concern.
Now this is the UK vaccine ... and the second such negative
journalist report on their vaccine in almost as many weeks. Is there
a pattern? No, but if one was a conspiracy theorist, one would be
having a great time. Many thanks to John for his detailed report.
-Mod.MHJ]
